ZH: 你们已经跑步多久了？
EN: How long have you been running?

ZH: 他们两个在一起多久了？
EN: How long have they been together?

ZH: 你打算在这个城市呆多久？
EN: How long do you plan to stay in this city?

ZH: 你能告诉我这个课程要学多久吗？
EN: Can you tell me how long this course will take to study?

ZH: 你想花多久时间写完这篇文章？
EN: How long do you want to spend writing this article?

ZH: 这家餐厅开得多久了？
EN: How long has this restaurant been open?

ZH: 你通常多久去一次健身房？
EN: How often do you go to the gym?

ZH: 他们要求你等多久？
EN: How long do they ask you to wait?

ZH: 这个项目预计要多久完成？
EN: How long is this project expected to take to complete?

ZH: 你上次看医生是多久以前？
EN: How long ago did you see a doctor?

ZH: 你通常多久给父母打一次电话？
EN: How often do you call your parents?

ZH: 你打算等多久才买新手机？
EN: How long do you plan to wait before buying a new phone?

ZH: 你们通常多久去旅行一次？
EN: How often do you usually travel?

ZH: 请问邮件寄到国外需要多久？
EN: How long does it take for mail to be delivered internationally?

ZH: 你们公司的工程师培训要学多久？
EN: How long does it take for your company's engineers to be trained?

ZH: 谁能告诉我这本书的阅读时间有多久？
EN: Who can tell me how long it takes to read this book?

ZH: 这道菜要烹饪多久？
EN: How long does it take to cook this dish?

ZH: 你可以告诉我图书馆关门要多久吗？
EN: Can you tell me how long the library closes?

ZH: 他们的演出要进行多久？
EN: How long will their performance last?

ZH: 昨天我学习了多久？
EN: How long did I study yesterday?
